(2,	2,	5296856629293,	'3 is a charm ring silver',	'<p>This little charming ring fits everything. Stack it up with some other wild rings or wear it on its own. You can do whatever you want with this beauty. </p>\n<p><span>This is a </span><em><strong>ring finger ring</strong></em></p>\n<p>Handmade in Bali <br> Material: sterling silver 925<br> Also available in <a href=\"https://wildthings-collectables.com/products/3-is-a-charm-ring-gold\">gold</a></p>\n<p><strong>Sizes (inside diameter)<br></strong><span>1 (16.5mm / US 6)</span><br><span>2 (16.9mm / US 6.5 )</span><br><span>3  (17.4mm / US 7 )</span></p>\n<p>Not sure what your ring size is? Have a look at our <a href=\"https://wildthings-collectables.com/pages/ring-sizes\">size chart</a> to find the right size</p>',	'Wildthings_collectables',	'Ring',	'2021-01-30 08:33:47',	'2021-09-16 01:21:53',	'3-is-a-charm-ring-silver',	'1',	'@3-is-a-charm-ring-gold, @stacking-ring, new added, ring-finger:ring',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0336/6977/5405/products/Wildthings-Collectables-rings-3-is-a-charm-silver.jpg?v=1620385509',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38'),
