(4,	2,	5296861544493,	'Aqua bay bracelet silver',	'<p>How stunning is this new color? All the beads are handmade from recycled glass and unique. It\'s a color to steal the show with, but also perfect to blend in with other bracelets.</p>\n<p>Handmade in Bali<br> Materials: Recycled glass and sterling silver<br> Measurements: 17,5 cm + 2,5cm extender<br> Also available in <a href=\"https://wildthings-collectables.com/collections/bracelets/products/aqua-bay-bracelet-gold\">gold</a></p>',	'wildthings_collectables',	'Bracelet',	'2021-01-30 08:38:10',	'2021-06-26 07:16:09',	'aqua-bay-bracelet-silver',	'1',	'@aqua-bay-bracelet-gold, @golden-bay-set-silver, bracelet, Green Ocean, new added, silver',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0336/6977/5405/products/04.Wildthings-Collectables-bracelets-aqua-bay-silver.jpg?v=1612349484',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38'),
(5,	2,	5296860332077,	'Aqua bay drop earring silver',	'<p>Its green, it\'s fresh, it\'s bright. We are in love with this earring and could wear this forever and ever. What else can we say? Combine this beauty with the ice star earcuff for a perfect color combination.</p>\n<p>*These earrings are sold per piece, so if you would like two of them make sure you add two to your basket.</p>\n<p>Handmade in Bali<br> Materials: Sterling silver<br> Measurements: hoop: 12mm diameter - charm: 8mm x 3mm<br> Also available in <a href=\"https://wildthings-collectables.com/collections/earrings/products/aqua-bay-drop-earring-gold\">gold</a></p>',	'wildthings_collectables',	'Earring',	'2021-01-30 08:37:09',	'2021-06-26 07:16:09',	'aqua-bay-drop-earring-silver',	'1',	'@aqua-bay-drop-earring-gold, earing-qty:single, earring, earring-type:hoop, Green Ocean, new added, silver',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0336/6977/5405/products/32.Wildthings-Collectables-earrings-aqua-bay-drop-silver_6b69146d-2d71-4bf6-bbbb-40943c4c46e1.jpg?v=1612349488',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38'),
