(8,	2,	5296861642797,	'Aqua set gold',	'<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">These beauty\'s are a mix of two of our loveliest necklaces. We love this set because of all the details. You can go all out with this set!</p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Handmade in Bali<br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"> Material: 18k gold plated brass<br><br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"> This set consists of:<br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"> 1 x aqua bay necklace gold - €59,95<br>Necklace length is 34cm+5cm extender</p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">1 x water ripple necklace- €79,90<br>Necklace length 45 cm<span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">+5cm extender</span></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong>Buying this set will save you 5%</strong></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">*It is possible to return one item of this set</p>',	'Wildthings_collectables',	'Necklace',	'2021-01-30 08:38:15',	'2021-06-26 07:16:12',	'aqua-set-gold',	'1',	'gold, Green Ocean, necklace, set',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0336/6977/5405/products/Aquaset.jpg?v=1620703958',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38'),
(9,	2,	5296858431533,	'Aquamarine Pebble ring gold',	'<p>Let the bomb drop: Remember last season’s Pebble Ring? Here comes the even more perfect version. The rich-in-colour stone carefully integrated into this Pebble ring radiates style and taste like no other. Aquamarine stone is often used to relax and cleanse from the old.</p>\n<p>We love to stack three or four of them on one finger and combine different colours. Or add the normal Pebble ring if you like it more quiet. Anyway, this look is seriously wild!</p>\n<p>This is a <strong>ring finger ring.</strong></p>\n<p>Handmade in Bali<br>Material: 18k gold plated brass and Aquamarine colored stone<br>Also available in silver</p>\n<p><strong>Sizes (inside diameter):</strong><br>1 (16.5mm / US 6)<br>2 (16.9mm / US 6.5) <br>3 (17.4mm / US 7)</p>\n<p>Not sure what your ring size is? Have a look at our size chart to find the right size.﻿</p>',	'wildthings_collectables',	'Ring',	'2021-01-30 08:35:35',	'2021-06-26 07:16:13',	'aquamarine-pebble-ring-gold',	'1',	'@aquamarine-pebble-ring-silver, @stacking-ring, citrine-pebble-ring-gold, New_added_lartiste, pebble-ring-gold, ring-finger:ring, tourmaline-pebble-ring-gold, video#https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1604/6741/files/aquamarine-pebble-ring-gold.mp4?v=1595499717, white-zirconia-pebble-ring-gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0336/6977/5405/products/Wildthings-Collectables-rings-aquamarine-pebble-gold.jpg?v=1612349520',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38'),
