(11,	2,	5296860561453,	'As cold as ice pendant gold',	'<p>Remember we captivated a cloud in our previous collection? Well, we all loved it so much that we couldn\'t miss it in this collection. This time we caught some ice for you, how \'cool\' is that?</p>\n<p>*If you would like to wear the pendant and necklace together make sure you select the option *set* in the menu above. This pendant comes with the Figaro choker (36cm).<br></p>\n<p>Handmade in Bali<br> Materials: 18k gold plated brass and resin<br> Measurements: width: 1,5cm height: 1cm<br> Also available in <a href=\"https://wildthings-collectables.com/collections/necklaces/products/as-cold-as-ice-pendant-silver\">silver</a></p>',	'wildthings_collectables',	'Pendant',	'2021-01-30 08:37:22',	'2021-06-26 07:16:15',	'as-cold-as-ice-pendant-gold',	'1',	'@as-cold-as-ice-pendant-silver, gold, Green Ocean, necklace, necklace-type:pendant, new added, pendant, video#https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1604/6741/files/blauwe_outfit_storie_formaat.mp4?v=1605096901',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0336/6977/5405/products/05.Wildthings-Collectables-pendants-as-cold-as-ice-single-gold.jpg?v=1611999442',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38',	'2021-09-20 04:29:38'),
