(68,	3,	6719868731569,	'PEARL CONTINUITY NECKLACE',	'<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<p>Strikingly minimal in its design, the Pearl Continuity necklace is as beautiful on bare skin as it is layered over a tee or lightweight turtleneck. The gentle curves of its hand-formed circle and single pink pearl remind us of our favorite inspiration, the graceful strength of feminine energy and the natural curves of the female form. The longest necklace in the collection, it is a soulful statement piece whose simplicity of design makes it perfect to treasure and wear for years. </p>\n<div>- 14k recycled gold -<br>- 8mm freshwater pearl -<br>\n<div>- 20<span>\" long, lobster clasp closure</span><span> </span>-<br>- High polish finish -<br>- Handmade to order, please allow 5-7 business days to ship -<br><br><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<span>Shop for this product and more </span><a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">directly from White/Space</a><span>.</span>\n</div>\n</div>',	'WHITE/SPACE',	'Necklace',	'2021-05-14 04:47:58',	'2021-06-23 19:29:27',	'pearl-continuity-necklace',	'1',	'14k, gold, necklace, pearl, recycled gold, yellow gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0545/5314/9617/products/shop.continuity_nklc_front_1024x1024_e1c23a34-0a14-4eee-8001-3379b254778f.jpg?v=1620974879',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15'),
