(76,	3,	6719867682993,	'SCARPA DIAMOND EARRINGS',	'<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<div>An elegant study in the beauty of repetition, and the interplay of light and line, these earrings are inspired by the work of Italian modernist architect and designer,<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/blogs/journal/carlo-scarpa\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Carlo Scarpa Modernist design inspiration\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Carlo Scarpa</a>.  At once static and in subtle motion, two overlapping circles are accented by a delicate diamond that swings ever so slightly from the center - just enough to give a subtle sparkle when worn. </div>\n<div>Sold as a pair, choose between 14k yellow, rose or white gold.</div>\n<div>\n<br>- 1.25\" long, a little under 1\" wide -<br>- Post back for pierced ears -<br>- 2mm diamonds, .06tcw, VS clarity, G-H color -<br>- High polish finish -<br>- Made to order, please allow 7-10 business days to ship -<br><br><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<span>Shop for this product and more </span><a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">directly from White/Space</a><span>.</span>\n</div>',	'WHITE/SPACE',	'Earring',	'2021-05-14 04:47:24',	'2021-06-24 14:16:21',	'scarpa-diamond-earrings',	'1',	'14k, diamonds, earrings, gold, recycled gold, rose gold, studs, white gold, yellow gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0545/5314/9617/products/SHOP.SCARPA_W_DIAM_YG_1024x1024_9c20ac3c-3142-4d84-a3e1-f0e623f6bd5b.png?v=1620974844',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15'),
