(80,	3,	6719866962097,	'SOLO NECKLACE, OPAL',	'<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<div>Slightly larger than the diamond versions, this opal necklace has just the right amount of iridescence. The chain slides through a minimal tube, upon which a 4mm opal shows off it\'s variable hues.  Please note each opal is slightly different, making each necklace unique.  The exact balance of hues may differ from those pictured.  Available in 14k yellow gold.</div>\n<div>This necklace is 16\" long and meant to be worn close to the collarbone.</div>\n<div>\n<br>- 14k recycled gold -<br>- 4mm Opal -<br>- High polish finish -<br>- Handmade to order, please allow 3-5 business days to ship -<br><br><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<span>Shop for this product and more </span><a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">directly from White/Space</a><span>.</span>\n</div>',	'WHITE/SPACE',	'Necklace',	'2021-05-14 04:47:03',	'2021-06-24 14:16:22',	'solo-necklace-opal',	'1',	'14k, gold, necklace, opal, recycled gold, yellow gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0545/5314/9617/products/SOLO_NKLC_OPAL165_DPI_1024x1024_a1054967-e6c4-4e9f-89a0-79c587332a25.png?v=1620974823',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15'),
