(82,	3,	6719866601649,	'STICK CHAIN STUD EARRING',	'<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<div>Modern and super cool, gold chain wraps around the earlobe from skinny gold bars. They look delicate, but our sticks are made ever so slightly thicker (so they don\'t bend!)  These are great for mixing and matching with other chain stud shapes or other earrings to make a unique earstack, so they\'re<span> </span><strong>sold as singles</strong>.   Available in 14k Yellow Gold or Sterling Silver with choice of metal backs. </div>\n<br>\n<div> - 3/4\" bar -<br> - Recycled 14k Gold or Sterling Silver -<br>\n<div>\n<strong>- Sold Individually, for a pair please select 2 -</strong><br> - High polish finish -<br> - Handmade to order, please allow 7 business days to ship -<br><br><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<span>Shop for this product and more </span><a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">directly from White/Space</a><span>.</span>\n</div>\n</div>',	'WHITE/SPACE',	'Earring',	'2021-05-14 04:46:52',	'2021-06-25 11:47:34',	'stick-chain-stud-earring',	'1',	'14k, earrings, gold, recycled gold, sterling silver, studs, yellow gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0545/5314/9617/products/shop.stick-chain-stud_RESIZE_1024x1024_58b3bcba-b1e3-4cb3-9c56-3be68c6f12bf.jpg?v=1620974812',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15'),
(83,	3,	6719866503345,	'TREVISO EARRINGS',	'<!--Start tab labels-->\n<ul class=\"tabs\">\n<li><a class=\"active\" href=\"#tab1\">Details</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tab2\">Shipping</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tab3\">Source</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!--Start tab content-->\n<ul class=\"tabs-content\">\n<li class=\"active\" id=\"tab1\">\n<p>A luminescent pink pearl sits balanced on the edge of a curved gold bar.  Bold, yet delicate, these earrings are a perfect example of the versatility and beauty of minimalist design.</p>\n<span>- Approximately 38mm (1.5\") tall -</span><br><span>- 8mm freshwater pink pearl -</span><br><span>- Recycled 14k Gold -</span><br><span>- Wear curved to the front or back -</span><br><span>- High polish finish -</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"tab2\">\n<p><span>- Handmade to order, please allow 5-7 business days to ship -<br><br></span></p>\n</li>\n<li id=\"tab3\">\n<p><span>Shop for this product and more <a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">directly from White/Space</a>.<br></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>',	'WHITE/SPACE',	'Earring',	'2021-05-14 04:46:49',	'2021-06-24 14:16:22',	'treviso-earrings',	'1',	'14k, drop earrings, earrings, gold, pearl, recycled gold, sterling silver, yellow gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0545/5314/9617/products/SHOP.TREVISO_PAIR_FRONT_NO_SHADOW_SILVER_1024x1024_e655b7bb-eca8-4afb-8556-916d286c071a.png?v=1620974809',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15'),
(84,	3,	6719866372273,	'VERITTI PEARL HOOK EARRING',	'<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<div class=\"product-description rte\" itemprop=\"description\">\n<div>The Veritti hook is a whole new way of wearing an earring. A 2.5mm conflict-free diamond and an 8mm pink pearl hang on a solid 14k gold threader earring.  To wear this earring, the pearl screws off, the hook is threaded through the ear, and then the pearl is securely screwed back on.</div>\n<div>Available in 14k yellow gold.<span> </span><strong>Sold as a single, for a pair please choose 2.</strong><br><br>- 2.25\" back hang length, 1\" front hang length -<br>- Recycled 14k Gold  -<br>- 2.5mm (.06ct each) conflict-free white diamond -<br>- High polish finish -<br>- Handmade to order, please allow 7 business days to ship -<br><br><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<span>Shop for this product and more </span><a href=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">directly from White/Space</a><span>.</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"offers\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Offer\">\n<form method=\"post\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\" id=\"AddToCartForm-{{ section.id }\" data-section=\"product\" class=\"product-form-product product-form\" action=\"https://www.whitespacejewelry.com/cart/add\">\n<div class=\"selector-wrapper js\"></div>\n</form>\n</div>',	'WHITE/SPACE',	'Earring',	'2021-05-14 04:46:44',	'2021-06-25 11:47:34',	'veritti-pearl-hook-earring',	'1',	'14k, diamond, earrings, gold, pearl, recycled gold, threaders, white diamond, yellow gold',	'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0545/5314/9617/products/VERITTI_NO_SHADOW_single_1024x1024_55778ef3-9812-4497-a2aa-c050a6b1c491.png?v=1620974804',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15',	'2021-09-20 04:35:15'),
